      "writtenOn": "2016-07-19T16:56:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Would it make sense not to send the PID?  I should have commented on the other CL -- it\u0027s a little confusing to send something specific like the result of getpid() when you\u0027re not actually using it.  It seems like it might be an important part of the algorithm.  Maybe the guest should just send a known constant, like, say, 100, which you could assert you receive here.",
